{"tid":2461450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Skechers 調查後表示新疆勞工好自由 會照用新疆綿","createTime":"2021-03-25T12:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T12:35:21.000Z","uid":10392,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0178545abbb139b10ce68a9a906a7dd2ccbb035e","tid":2461450,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"殘體link <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/gn/2021-03-25/detail-ikkntiam8185198.d.html?isJump=0&amp;universallink=1&amp;from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fgn%2F2021-03-25%2Fdetail-ikkntiam8185198.d.html%3FisJump%3D0%26universallink%3D1%26from%3Dwap&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=87b69888\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/gn/2021-03-25/detail-ikkntiam8185198.d.html?isJump=0&amp;universallink=1&amp;from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄：<br />\n近日，Skechers在官網發佈了一則聲明被網友找到，在ASPI污蔑新疆「強迫勞動」報告發佈後，它第一時間和供應方取得聯繫，瞭解真實情況。<br />\n<br />\n記者在Skechers英文網站找到了這則聲明<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ4TFfVBziFoBdGBetY61d3o522JNKZvjkg1poeoSsv2X?filename=Xh4GbAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXh4GbAL.jpg&h=9f897dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSkechers从亚洲的许多工厂和供应商那里获得消息，包括ASPI认定的位于东莞的绿洲鞋厂（以下简称绿洲），在得知报告中的指控后，Skechers立刻检查了其内部记录， Skechers还确认，按照常规做法，Skechers在2017年，2018年，2019年和2020年對綠洲進行了多次審查，包括已宣佈和未宣佈的審查，並且這些審查均未顯示出使用強迫勞動或其他有關勞動條件的跡象。<br />\n<br />\n自《 ASPI報告》發佈以來，Skechers對綠洲進行了兩次審查，這些審查都沒有發現維吾爾族或任何其他種族或宗教團體使用強迫勞動的跡象，也沒有引起其他對一般勞動條件的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n最近，綠洲為Skechers提供了一份補充的《社會責任聲明》，專門闡述並保證平等對待包括維吾爾族在內的所有少數民族，以平等，公正和透明的方式對待所有工人。基於這些事實，Skechers沒有理由相信綠洲在使用任何強迫勞動。儘管如此，Skechers仍將繼續密切監視和審查綠洲以及全球所有工廠和供應商。<br />\n<br />\nSkechers 原link<br />\n<a href=\"https://about.skechers.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/SKECHERS-USA-STATEMENT-UYGHURS-March-2021.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabout.skechers.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FSKECHERS-USA-STATEMENT-UYGHURS-March-2021.pdf&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=e4744bbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://about.skechers.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/SKECHERS-USA-STATEMENT-UYGHURS-March-2021.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"2ce342d93c2079745c1d452db91c9e6699190978","tid":2461450,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e01fac9f01ab134b486fadaf0d5cfd4d676c6a1","tid":2461450,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"好少幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1f218df644f8aebfb6283223dc512908f8dd61","tid":2461450,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"有啲唔記得轉繁體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb9f1046edafd971b78c74b43e3a5780087db23","tid":2461450,"uid":180402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"款太柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19764e8bb95d8a1fad6d5e392b76d267a64d5db","tid":2461450,"uid":10392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbb9f1046edafd971b78c74b43e3a5780087db23","tid":2461450,"uid":180402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"款太柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:15:29.000Z","msg":"之前有一對<br />\n覺得都算舒服<br />\n但估唔到美國公司都跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef91da8c2f1838bccbe317495f453e19f3ca919d","tid":2461450,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T12:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.